snippet.title: Game Party Champions - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment announces Game Party Champions, an engaging game for all ages, is available today exclusively for Wii U™.  The latest iteration of the hugely successful Game Party franchise, the game offers players new ways to compete in arcade, sports and party games by tilting, turning and swiping the Wii U™ GamePad touch screen controller.
